# ✦ PocketCam Firmware Flowcharts 📷🐻

## Main System Process

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A([Power On]) --> B[Display PocketCam Startup Screen]
    B --> C[Initialise Camera]
    C --> D{Camera Working?}

    D -- No --> E[Display Camera Error]
    E --> F[Retry Initialisation]
    F --> C

    D -- Yes --> G[Initialise microSD Card]
    G --> H{SD Card Detected?}

    H -- No --> I[Display SD Card Error]
    I --> J[Retry SD Initialisation]
    J --> G

    H -- Yes --> K[Find Next Photo Number]
    K --> L[Display Ready Screen]

    L --> M{User Action}

    M -- Press Shutter --> N[Capture Photograph]
    M -- Open Gallery --> O[Start Offline Wi-Fi Gallery]
    M -- Open Menu --> P[Display Camera Settings]

    N --> Q{Image Captured?}

    Q -- No --> R[Display Capture Error]
    R --> L

    Q -- Yes --> S[Generate JPEG Filename]
    S --> T[Save Photograph to microSD]
    T --> U{Photo Saved?}

    U -- No --> V[Display Storage Error]
    V --> L

    U -- Yes --> W[Increase Photo Counter]
    W --> X[Display Photo Saved]
    X --> L

    O --> Y[Allow Phone to View and Download Photos]
    Y --> L

    P --> L
```